<p> <i>Summary</i> 
</p>
<p> The present report contains the Special Rapporteur&#8217;s observations on 
</p>
<p>communications sent to States between 16 March 2011 and 15 March 2012, as well as on 
</p>
<p>responses received from States in relation to these communications until 15 May 2012. 
</p>
